com.camerontec.catalys.util.fast

Class SampleFastCompatibleMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.fast.SampleFastCompatibleMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBindable<ListIterator<ITagValue>>, IFastDecodableMessage, IFastEncodableMessage

    public class SampleFastCompatibleMessage
extends Object
implements IFastEncodableMessage, IFastDecodableMessage
    Very simple implementation of a message which can be encoded and decoded using our FAST libraries.

    It is not intended as an efficient message format. It is designed to be as light weight as possible for the purposes of performance testing.

    However, note that this implementation does follow the guidelines on object reuse described in the JavaDoc for the IFastDecodableMessage and IFastEncodableMessage interfaces.
